
---

# 2️⃣ `.gitignore` recommandé

Crée un fichier `.gitignore` à la racine du projet :

```gitignore
# Python
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo
*.pyd

# Virtual environment
venv/
.env/

# IDE
.vscode/
.idea/

# OS
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Python packaging
build/
dist/
*.egg-info/

# Logs
*.log

# Temporary files
*.tmp
*.swp

# Jupyter
.ipynb_checkpoints

# Docker
*.pid

# Database
*.db
*.sqlite

# Environment variables
.env

# Cache
.cache/

# Coverage
.coverage
htmlcov/